    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Hartford</placeName>
                <date>March 15/60</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><sic><addressee>Rev. Isaack Leeser</addressee></sic>!</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p>I send you herein enclosed<lb/> six dollars, for two years<lb/> subscription, for
                the<lb/> Occident it should have<lb/> been sent some time<lb/> since but I hope
                you<lb/> will pardon my negligence.<lb/> Supposing, that you feel<lb/> interested,
                in the prosperity<lb/> of our Congregation, I take<lb/> the Liberty to send you<lb/>
                herewith a copy, of the<lb/> statement, of our affairs,<lb/> which, I beg you to
                be</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>kind enough, to give place<lb/> in the <sic>colums</sic>, of your paper<lb/> I also
                send you herewith<lb/> a Copy, of a Barmizwa<lb/> Speech, of a Nephew, of mine,<lb/>
                which I would also like,<lb/> to see published, in your<lb/> valuable paper</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I remain yours respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Myer Stern</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
